  "original_title": "\u0baf\u0bbe\u0bb4\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba3\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb1\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bbf\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4 \u0b95\u0bca\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc8; \u0ba8\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bae\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0bb1\u0bae\u0bcd \u0b85\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0b9f\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Cruelty to girls in Jaffna; Court action",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Jaffna Magistrate's Court ordered the remand of five on charges of abducting two girls and having an inappropriate relationship in Jaffna.",
        "Also, the court yesterday ordered to keep both the girls who left the house in custody.",
        "Two weeks ago, two 17-year-old girls from Pudukudiripu left home and came to Jaffna and were at the bus station.",
        "A man who came to know about them took both the girls and stayed them in a hostel in Savagacherry.",
        "The three who left the hostel the day before yesterday came to the Jaffna bus station.",
        "That night, two bus drivers, two conductors and four other people took the girls into the forest in the forest.",
        "At that time one of the girls got down from the vehicle and came to the area where the people live.",
        "The girl who escaped reported the incident to passers-by and the police emergency department was informed.",
        "The five who went with the other girl brought her to Jaffna the next day and dropped her off.",
        "Based on the investigations conducted on the girls, the five were arrested on charges of abduction and indecent relationship."
      ],
